# LoreBoard - AI Agent Control UI

> A tabletop-style control interface for AI agent orchestration.

## Quick Start

```bash
cd loreboard-app
npm install
npm run dev
```

## Project Structure

```
lore-board/
├── loreboard-app/     # Vue 3 + Vite application
│   ├── src/
│   │   ├── components/
│   │   │   ├── Card.vue      # Resource card component
│   │   │   └── Verb.vue      # Action verb component
│   │   ├── App.vue           # Main tabletop canvas
│   │   └── main.js
│   ├── package.json
│   └── vite.config.js
├── types/              # Type definitions
├── core-mechanics.md   # Game mechanics documentation
├── README.md
└── TESTING_REQUIREMENTS.md
```

## Core Concepts

- **Drawer**: Resource library (infinite templates)
- **Tabletop**: Working area (card instances)
- **Verbs**: Action slots (study, work, explore)

## Tech Stack

- Vue 3 (Composition API)
- Vite 7
- Tailwind CSS v4

